Knights versus Warriors. No need to reply it again. <br>
<br>
Here a fictitious example :<br>
- old roster 14 warriors 4 Knights <br>
- new roster 8 warriors 10 Knights<br>
<br>
I believe the second setup would be more powerfull after the changes that VI<br>
did in the last 12 months. There is still a MT line of 8 warriors if defense is needed.<br>
10 Knights could help the raid more with uncurse, groupheals and offtanking as <br>
a warrior. If you take a look at Furors posting about the pure DPS in FoH you<br>
would not lost DPS. <br>
<br>
